DESCRIPTION
These Full Cheeks All-Natural Timothy Hay & Wood Treat & Chews are made with love for small animals like yours. These chews satisfy the natural instinct your small pet has to chew, and offers a satisfying crunch as well. We believe caring for your furry little one should be as easy as loving them, and now it can be. Our products are specially made for them, and are designed to be simple for you. All they need to do is what they do best: give lots of love. Only at PetSmart.

All-natural
Helps encourage chewing behaviors
Satisfying crunch of hay
3 Count
